Feature: Newsletter subscription


    Scenario: The newletter subscription link on the homepage should take me to the subscription form
        Given I am on the sukrupa.org home page
        When I follow the link to the subscription form
        Then I should be on the subscription form page

    Scenario: The newletter subscription link on the current news and blog page should take me to the subscription form
        Given I am on the sukrupa.org current news and blog page
        When I follow the link to the subscription form
        Then I should be on the subscription form page
